\begin_inset Formula $x>x''$
\end_inset

) where 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{A}G=0$
\end_inset

.
 The solutions in these regions are, as above, of the form: 
\begin_inset Formula \[
G_{\mbox{I}}=\alpha\sinh(\kappa x),\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula \[
G_{\mbox{III}}=\beta\sinh(\kappa(x-L)).\]

\end_inset

We require 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

