\begin_inset Formula \[
\alpha=\frac{\sinh(\kappa x'')/\kappa}{\sinh(\kappa x'')\cosh(\kappa x')-\cosh(\kappa x'')\sinh(\kappa x')}=\frac{\sinh(\kappa[L-x'])}{\kappa\sinh(\kappa L)},\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula \[
\beta=-\frac{\sinh(\kappa x')}{\kappa\sinh(\kappa L)},\]

\end_inset

using the identity 
\begin_inset Formula $\sinh(A-B)=\sinh(A)\cosh(B)-\cosh(A)\sinh(B)$
\end_inset

